snippet.textDisplay:
I think the voice that says 'The only thing they fear is you' may come from that one figure from the Urdak concept art. The voice sounds telepathic, which makes sense if it came from that figure as it has no lips and there's an implication that it's female as the Maykrs appear to be an all female faction and the colour scheme of the figure strongly resembles a shrine maiden.
Link to the concept art with the figure: https://images.ctfassets.net/rporu91m20dc/4jm2tqCRVDGWlKD2cA5K7t/e19887b7578ce7c8ecddb050af695fef/DE_The_Maykrs-Concept.jpg?q=70&fm=webp&w=1600&h=1600
